物，确认肥皂、牙膏、卫生纸的存量是否充足，并预先准备好炸酱、咖哩等三至四顿餐食，方便「不习惯做菜」的丈夫能简单加热食用。 除此之外，指南还要求准妈妈们预留三天至一星期的衣物，确保直到她们从医院返家之前，丈夫都有乾淨的内衣裤、袜子、衬衫、手帕可替换。指南甚至提醒孕妇产前记得买条髮带，「以免生产后看起来蓬头垢面」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8077806b755ff2bafa42c3d74c71cbbc_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "681 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439320796"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0OWWka/bvNxyEAMaCDU5OTA0OTEwIP+q//8FMBw4rAVABHIJNDM5MzIwNzk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1610941739.0976615", "card_id": "Q_374963188", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 170}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "潘博文事件真的是世界的 bug 么？潘博文这个人是否真实存在？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c4520f970f7403d37ce58b5095bfddf0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "548 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/374963188"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI0OWWka/bvNxyEAMaCDQ1NjAzNjUzIPGr2/IFMA843QNABXIJMzc0OTYzMTg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1610941739.098065", "card_id": "Q_434730115", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 597}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "穷破卖菜老人去银行存钱，银行发现假币后没收，老人在银行大厅痛哭，此时银行如何处理最好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很穷很老的卖菜老人去银行存钱，听到自己收的百元大钞是假的要被银行没收，崩溃的坐在银行地上大哭，哭诉自己卖菜挣钱不易。此时造成了大量群众围观议论，还有人拿出手机摄像，对银行的业务造成了影响。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-a68259c079346613ffd0fb59f022260f_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "419 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/434730115"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0OWWka/bvNxyEAMaCDU4ODg1NzA2IPG52f4FMGU46BFABnIJNDM0N